Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相聚一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.46,0:00:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想打從心裡大叫一句\N好想快點見到妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.38,0:00:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我相信總有一天\N一定能相遇相知永結連理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.22,0:00:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,起步走出\N希望妳能追著我的背影而來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.54,0:00:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我孤單一人只為等候妳的到來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.49,0:01:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,落英繽紛的春日午後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.56,0:01:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我將祈禱轉為誓言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.60,0:01:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但願妳不會忘記最重要的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.81,0:01:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,永遠閃亮動人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.10,0:01:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三鷹教練明天就要結婚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.47,0:01:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.54,0:01:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.61,0:01:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寫賀詞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.45,0:01:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,賀詞?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.55,0:01:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天三鷹教練\N就要結婚了不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.98,0:01:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以大家要在網球拍上\N各寫一句賀詞送給他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.42,0:01:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們兩位要不要寫?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.99,0:02:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好耶,那由管理員先寫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.26,0:02:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來吧\N妳應該有話想跟教練說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.03,0:02:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要寫什麼好呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.67,0:02:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寫一句怨恨他的話也好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.94,0:02:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比如說,你居然把我甩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.91,0:02:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼妳就不能誠心誠意\N為別人的幸福感到高興呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.12,0:02:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(祝你永遠幸福音無響子)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.56,0:03:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#95 啊～感動!\N包含於戒指中的奶奶之愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.33,0:03:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,讓我們暗地裡\N祝福三鷹的婚姻幸福美滿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.03,0:03:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乾杯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.40,0:03:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說喜宴在皇家飯店舉行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.57,0:03:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.37,0:03:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真想吃吃看\N一流飯店的法國料理的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.54,0:04:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說蜜月旅行是從希臘到西班牙\N環繞愛琴海一周呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.92,0:04:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員放棄他還真可惜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.79,0:04:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.46,0:04:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,究竟是什麼因緣\N怎麼會選到這個人呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.29,0:04:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用妳管!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.69,0:04:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了,管理員呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.53,0:04:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她好像在準備料理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.83,0:04:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姑且吃管理員的拿手好菜\N忍耐一下好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.27,0:04:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不想吃的話\N不吃也不要緊喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.54,0:04:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的耳朵什麼都聽不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.17,0:04:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒是五代\N你們進展到什麼地步了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.91,0:04:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們兩個…這個…那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.15,0:04:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想到哪裡去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.52,0:04:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是在問訂婚或結婚的日子\N你們多少應該有談一下吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.92,0:04:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有,還沒有談到那些事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.89,0:04:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過,管理員的爸媽\N已經答應了不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.30,0:04:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.46,0:04:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來輪到五代帶管理員\N去見你爸媽才對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.04,0:04:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.74,0:04:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的很沒用耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.87,0:05:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不快點的話\N說不定管理員會變心哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.35,0:05:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.72,0:05:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.55,0:05:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我正想把菜端過去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.29,0:05:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-那個…\N-什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.69,0:05:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…最近去一趟新瀉好不好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.30,0:05:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.43,0:05:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我希望妳能正式去見\N我爸媽還有奶奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.14,0:05:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.84,0:05:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳願意嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.91,0:05:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我願意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.81,0:05:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我現在馬上去打電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.45,0:05:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結婚?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.62,0:05:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊,裕作\N你幹得太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.16,0:05:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯,所以最近我想請個假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.30,0:06:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然這樣,打鐵要趁熱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.53,0:06:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天就回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.20,0:06:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.44,0:06:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明…明天?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.04,0:06:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起,我奶奶老是擅作主張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.08,0:06:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過,不一定非得明天去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.54,0:06:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳應該也有妳的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.35,0:06:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我什麼時候都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.82,0:06:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畢竟遲早都得要去拜訪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.56,0:06:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.62,0:06:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萬歲!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.36,0:06:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們都聽到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.93,0:06:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹的好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.53,0:06:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在幹嘛啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.97,0:06:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為你慢吞吞的\N所以我們才下樓來看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.03,0:06:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,這樣很好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.14,0:06:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀,等這個春天等得真久啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.94,0:06:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敲定了,今晚為了慶祝\N他們兩人要去新瀉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.31,0:06:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,痛痛快快喝一頓吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.19,0:07:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妝會不會太濃了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.53,0:07:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.04,0:07:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這件衣服不會太花俏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.74,0:07:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.02,0:07:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是說穿這一套比較好呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.82,0:07:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都很好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.86,0:07:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就麻煩你們看家囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.50,0:07:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請包在我們身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.13,0:07:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳就放心的去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.93,0:07:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幫我向奶奶問好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.27,0:07:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我們走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.34,0:07:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎,我們走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.58,0:07:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員不要緊吧\N她好像蠻緊張的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.01,0:08:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這也難怪,年紀比五代大\N而且又是再婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.99,0:08:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代本人是無所謂\N不過,他爸媽會答應嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.76,0:08:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畢竟鄉下人對這種事比較在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.46,0:08:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該沒問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.93,0:08:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果把朱美帶回家去\N他爸媽才會大吃一驚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.18,0:08:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.45,0:08:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我總覺得好緊張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.12,0:08:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你爸媽\N知道我全部的事情嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.19,0:08:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.39,0:08:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,例如我的年紀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.23,0:08:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有我是…第二次結婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.30,0:08:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別擔心,妳一定沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.71,0:09:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.71,0:09:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,是奶奶啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.65,0:09:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,五代他們已經出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.79,0:09:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?這真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.86,0:09:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會啊,當然會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.83,0:09:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.60,0:09:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼,再見囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.13,0:09:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰打來的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.94,0:09:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代的奶奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.44,0:09:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(湯之町車站)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.26,0:09:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會不會冷?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.79,0:09:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.19,0:09:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真奇怪\N奶奶應該會來接我們才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.10,0:09:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶,妳這是幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.54,0:10:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶,妳看起來好有精神哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.97,0:10:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好久不見了,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.01,0:10:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對,應該是我們家的響子\N歡迎妳來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.82,0:10:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.93,0:10:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們家就快到了哦,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.66,0:10:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.11,0:10:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是裕作出生長大的家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.72,0:10:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來,別客氣,進來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.99,0:10:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.56,0:10:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎光…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.03,0:11:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公\N裕作,裕作回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.20,0:11:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦,回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.77,0:11:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天為什麼還開門做生意?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.50,0:11:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難得響子專程來看你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.87,0:11:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,我沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.71,0:11:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳好妳好,一路上辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.81,0:11:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次真是麻煩妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.15,0:11:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,初次見面,我是音無響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.78,0:11:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說你們啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.78,0:11:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,你回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.12,0:11:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼我回來啦\N這麼重大的日子還開門做生意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.56,0:11:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們本來也是打算\N休息一天等你們回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.26,0:11:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是奶奶堅持\N一定要開店做生意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.06,0:11:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶,為什麼要這麼做?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.57,0:11:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼關係?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.40,0:11:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正響子\N要嫁到我們家做媳婦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.27,0:11:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又何必跟她那麼見外呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.44,0:11:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-對不對?\N-是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.61,0:11:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思沒什麼好招待的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.95,0:11:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的不要客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.35,0:11:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,豬排飯好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.98,0:11:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.79,0:11:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思,慌慌張張的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.36,0:11:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別那麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.49,0:12:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳好妳好,歡迎妳來我們家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.93,0:12:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伯父您好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.40,0:12:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩客炸蝦飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.70,0:12:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦,來了來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.37,0:12:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…我到店裡幫忙好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.27,0:12:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.28,0:12:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,這怎麼可以呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.04,0:12:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼關係,讓她去幫忙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.58,0:12:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.48,0:12:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.58,0:12:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊\N身體動一動也比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.79,0:12:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.49,0:12:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的很謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.65,0:12:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.72,0:12:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.19,0:12:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓她去忙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.69,0:12:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒是裕作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.93,0:12:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有很重要的事要跟你談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.61,0:12:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼重要的事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.85,0:13:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裕作,你有結婚資金嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.22,0:13:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳幹嘛突然問這個?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.09,0:13:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有還是沒有?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.69,0:13:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才剛找到工作而已\N接下來會慢慢存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.53,0:13:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想讓響子等到\N你存夠錢為止嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.87,0:13:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個拿去用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.27,0:13:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是這是奶奶的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.51,0:13:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要管,拿去用就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.18,0:13:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等你存夠錢娶老婆\N我得活到一百歲才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.52,0:13:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是給我這麼大一筆錢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.98,0:13:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰說要給你的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.65,0:13:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我存起來要當棺材本的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.23,0:13:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我死之前要還給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.50,0:13:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.87,0:13:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定會給妳辦一個\N非常風光的葬禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.27,0:13:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就不能說點中聽的話嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.17,0:13:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.31,0:14:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請用茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.58,0:14:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們請了新人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.38,0:14:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是,她是裕作未來的老婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.05,0:14:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.48,0:14:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦,真是個大美人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.95,0:14:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.82,0:14:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.16,0:14:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣也省得去跟街坊鄰居介紹\N真好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.13,0:14:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊,還是奶奶聰明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.97,0:14:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,炸天婦羅飯和南蠻咖哩飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.50,0:14:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,炸天婦羅飯和南蠻咖哩飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.84,0:14:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.81,0:14:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裕作,你在做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.64,0:14:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒…沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.01,0:14:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好像很閒哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.21,0:14:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞什麼啊\N我回來不是為了做這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.15,0:14:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.49,0:14:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦,你們來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.16,0:14:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由加里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.26,0:14:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們來看妳的孫媳婦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.79,0:14:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.99,0:14:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.40,0:14:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是裕作的新娘子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.77,0:14:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.97,0:15:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇,好漂亮哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.27,0:15:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的,簡直像個洋娃娃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.28,0:15:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天晚上我請客\N大家別客氣儘管吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.66,0:15:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好耶,好耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.46,0:15:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.19,0:15:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.60,0:15:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,介紹新娘子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.06,0:15:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是太好了,小裕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.20,0:15:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真是好福氣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.40,0:15:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.24,0:15:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.54,0:15:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.88,0:15:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,裕作,還有一個外送
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.98,0:15:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次是三丁目的村野家\N兩碗天婦羅蕎麥麵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.72,0:15:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託,你們也關心一下響子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.79,0:15:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也想那麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.29,0:15:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是順著奶奶的意思吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.52,0:15:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畢竟不曉得她老人家\N什麼時候會走啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.09,0:15:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼又說這種話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.00,0:16:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.93,0:16:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳這個孫媳婦\N真是又賢慧又美麗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.94,0:16:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(本日已打烊)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.58,0:16:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.28,0:16:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她跟奶奶到二樓去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.05,0:16:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二樓?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.19,0:16:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,店裡我來整理\N裕作,你也去休息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.09,0:16:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我年輕時\N爺爺送給我的戒指
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.50,0:16:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然不值錢,這個給妳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.27,0:16:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這怎麼可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.67,0:16:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是奶奶最珍貴的紀念品\N不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.37,0:16:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎麼可以收下呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.44,0:16:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.48,0:16:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到別的地方去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.18,0:16:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.58,0:16:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少廢話,走開啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.89,0:17:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個戒指啊,我早就決定\N要送給裕作的新娘子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.33,0:17:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳就當作是我的遺物\N收下來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.40,0:17:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶,妳怎麼這麼說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.34,0:17:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裕作是我親手帶大的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.18,0:17:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然他很迷糊,又靠不住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.68,0:17:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卻是我全心栽培的好孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.15,0:17:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請妳一定要好好照顧他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.69,0:17:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才要請他多照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.32,0:17:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝奶奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.43,0:17:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼,妳願意收下這個戒指囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.47,0:17:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的,謝謝奶奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.24,0:17:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裕作,裕作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.01,0:17:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹嘛啦,一下子趕我出去\N一下子又叫我進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.08,0:17:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少囉嗦,坐下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.18,0:18:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把這個戒指\N戴在響子的手指上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.92,0:18:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個戒指哪來的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.22,0:18:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要問那麼多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.46,0:18:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,總算完成了一樁心事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.10,0:18:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.00,0:18:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.97,0:18:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.14,0:18:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.54,0:18:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.98,0:19:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶,妳怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.11,0:19:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.52,0:19:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.28,0:19:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.98,0:19:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶,妳醒一醒啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.92,0:19:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶,奶奶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.35,0:19:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.53,0:19:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開玩笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.13,0:19:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在抱到曾孫之前\N我怎麼可以死呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.67,0:19:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且也沒喪葬費
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.84,0:19:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳這個滿臉皺紋的臭奶奶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.91,0:19:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的很不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.98,0:19:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳真的好窩心哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.38,0:19:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有,您太誇獎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.82,0:19:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裕作,你找到了一個好老婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.62,0:19:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.06,0:19:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我這個不成材的兒子,今後…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.52,0:19:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還請妳多多關照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.39,0:19:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別這麼說,請多多關照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.80,0:19:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於比較像樣點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.60,0:19:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她都來這麼久了,你們還在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.27,0:20:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今晚要好好的來\N提前慶祝一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.24,0:20:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,難得裕作帶新娘子回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.38,0:20:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去做點小菜來吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.65,0:20:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-來\N-謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.15,0:20:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-請\N-謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.36,0:20:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好慢哦,到底在搞什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.66,0:20:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像有人來了\N裕作,你去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.57,0:20:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.24,0:20:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.84,0:20:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經打烊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.38,0:20:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,幫我們開門啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.28,0:20:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慶祝喜事當然人多才熱鬧啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.55,0:20:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今晚要喝個痛快,喝個過癮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.62,0:20:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說裕作一直受到你們照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.49,0:20:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能住在他隔壁房\N也算是一種緣分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.23,0:20:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來,伯父,多喝一點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.60,0:20:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.53,0:21:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來來,管理員和五代\N你們要笑一笑,笑得開心一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.67,0:21:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了你們充滿希望的未來\N整晚來喝賞雪酒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.98,0:21:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣跟在一刻館有什麼兩樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.45,0:21:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦,酒在這裡喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.55,0:21:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪,響子呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.76,0:21:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她不在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.97,0:21:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裕作,祝你17歲生日快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.48,0:21:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是奶奶送我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.21,0:21:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過,幾乎都沒看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.48,0:21:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起,擅自進來你的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.09,0:21:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.32,0:21:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過,這個房間很單調吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.92,0:22:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才不會呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.19,0:22:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代\N你一直住在這個房間嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.10,0:22:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,一直到高中畢業\N搬去一刻館為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.84,0:22:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.25,0:22:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是和橄欖球社的人一起照的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.85,0:22:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然大家都在笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.32,0:22:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實是慘敗的時候照的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.39,0:22:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是看起來真的很開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.38,0:22:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你每天都看著\N這個城鎮的風景生活啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.78,0:22:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.22,0:23:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好美哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.00,0:23:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.40,0:23:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,你在哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.97,0:23:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦,原來你們在這裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.28,0:23:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們怎麼隨便跑進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.41,0:23:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們來看\N你們在做什麼好事啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.15,0:23:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼好事?我也要看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.08,0:23:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.95,0:23:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來,慶祝他們兩人的婚事\N喝個痛快吧,喝個過癮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.32,0:23:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好耶,好耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.92,0:23:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們不要鬧了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.06,0:23:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來,裕作,你也喝你也喝…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.83,0:23:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這兩年好長哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.24,0:23:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於有了結局了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.27,0:23:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼\N祝五代和管理員幸福美滿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.87,0:24:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也祝全國的相聚一刻影迷健康
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.48,0:24:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乾杯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.88,0:24:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.35,0:24:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「只要這份愛還在!\N永遠的一刻館!」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.19,0:24:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Begin the night
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.89,0:24:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Begin your love
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.13,0:24:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳該知道這不是擦身而過的戀情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.07,0:24:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,親吻也是…woo
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.24,0:24:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳比我想像中冷淡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.42,0:24:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喜歡一個人獨處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:43.12,0:24:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沉默不語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:48.02,0:24:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要逞強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:51.70,0:24:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這燭火依偎著的夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:01.94,0:25:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凝視著妳的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:08.81,0:25:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,試著將至今的謊言吹熄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:16.69,0:25:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Begin the night
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:20.42,0:25:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Begin your love
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:23.63,0:25:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自我陶醉故弄玄虛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:27.93,0:25:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對我行不通…woo

